                            </div>

                            <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>A VPS is a virtual private server that can run anything a linux server can - including online shops, written content, media content, and/or software applications, primarily web applications - portals, extranets, collaborative solutions, wiki, CRM, etc. </p>
